OL,3,CRail fares in England to increase by
OL,4,C4.9% next year
OL,6,FRail fares in England will increase by
OL,7,Fup to 4.9% from March 3 next year, the
OL,8,FDepartment for Transport has said.
OL,10,FThe cap regulates the price increase
OL,11,Ffor season tickets on most commuter
OL,12,Fjourneys, some off-peak return tickets
OL,13,Fon long-distance routes and flexible
OL,14,Ftickets for travel around major cities.
OL,16,FJuly's RPI measure of inflation, which
OL,17,Fis traditionally used to determine
OL,18,Fannual fare rises, was 9.0%.
OL,20,FThe previous cap on increases in
OL,21,Fregulated fares was 5.9%.
